a.','[\"Mount Kailash\", \"Lake Mansarovar\", \"Potala Palace\", \"Jokhang Temple\"]','May-Sep','3,656m','Moderate to Challenging','/destinations/tibet',6,'[317, 314, 13, 11, 315, 316]','[6, 5]',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1,'2026-07-05 20:11:55','2026-07-05 20:11:55',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(6,16,'lumbini','Lumbini','Lumbini','Nepal',NULL,'nepal','/uploads/destinations/lumbini/lumbini_1766899454279.avif','Discover the beauty and culture of Lumbini in Nepal.','[]','Mar-May, Sep-Nov','Varies','Easy','/destinations/lumbini',2,'[29, 306]','[]',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1,'2026-07-05 20:11:55','2026-07-05 20:11:55',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(7,17,'vietnam','Vietnam','Vietnam','Viet Nam',NULL,'international','/uploads/destinations/vietnam/vietnam_1769503837496.jpg','Discover the beauty and culture of Vietnam in Viet Nam.','[]','Year-round','Varies','Easy to Moderate','/destinations/vietnam',1,'[328]','[]',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1,'2026-07-05 20:11:55','2026-07-05 20:11:55',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(8,23,'mustang-region','Muktinath','Muktinath','Nepal',NULL,'nepal','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506905925346-21bda4d32df4?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop','Discover the beauty and culture of Muktinath in Nepal.','[\"Upper Mustang\", \"Lo Manthang\", \"Muktinath Temple\", \"Tibetan Culture\"]','Mar-Nov','3,800m','Moderate','/destinations/mustang-region',2,'[7, 309]','[]',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1,'2026-07-05 20:11:55','2026-07-05 20:11:55',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(9,26,'dubai','Dubai','Dubai','UAE',NULL,'international','/uploads/destinations/dubai/dubai_1766145747532.jpg','Discover the beauty and culture of Dubai in UAE.','[\"Burj Khalifa\", \"Dubai Mall\", \"Desert Safari\", \"Palm Jumeirah\", \"Dubai Marina\", \"Gold Souk\", \"Atlantis Resort\", \"Dubai Fountain\"]','Nov-Mar','Sea Level','Easy','/destinations/dubai',3,'[202, 203, 201]','[8, 9, 10]',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1,'2026-07-05 20:11:55','2026-07-05 20:11:55',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(10,28,'annapurna-','Annapurna ','Annapurna ','Nepal',NULL,'nepal','/uploads/destinations/annapurna-/annapurna-_1762006248934.jpeg','Annapurna Region','[]','Year-round','Varies','Easy to Moderate','/destinations/annapurna-',1,'[312]','[]',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1,'2026-07-05 20:11:55','2026-07-05 20:11:55',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(11,30,'thailand','Thailand','Thailand','Thailand',NULL,'international','/uploads/destinations/thailand/thailand_1766316382659.jpg','Discover the beauty and culture of Thailand in Thailand.','[]','Year-round','Varies','Easy to Moderate','/destinations/thailand',3,'[319, 320, 329]','[]',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1,'2026-07-05 20:11:55','2026-07-06 07:33:50','Plan Thailand with clarity around Bangkok city stays, island holidays, family trips, honeymoon-style travel and Thailand–Malaysia–Singapore combinations from Nepal.','November to March is the most popular period; beach routes can vary by coast and season.','Thailand works well for short holidays, honeymoon-style travel and add-on routes with Malaysia or Singapore. The biggest planning mistake is choosing hotels and transfers before understanding the travel pace.','[{\"body\": \"Bangkok, Pattaya, Phuket, Krabi and island routes offer different travel experiences. The best choice depends on budget, group type, transfer tolerance and whether the trip is for leisure, family or celebration.\", \"icon\": \"MapPin\", \"title\": \"Choose the right base\"}, {\"body\": \"A short Thailand tour should avoid too many hotel changes. We help structure days so sightseeing, airport transfers, beach time and optional activities feel smooth instead of rushed.\", \"icon\": \"Route\", \"title\": \"Balance pace and transfers\"}, {\"body\": \"Travellers from Nepal often need clarity on documents, hotel area, pickup timing, local support and how to combine Thailand with nearby destinations. These details should be solved before payment.\", \"icon\": \"Shield\", \"title\": \"Plan support before booking\"}]','[{\"answer\": \"A short Bangkok or Pattaya trip can work in 4–5 days, while beach routes or multi-country combinations usually need 7–10 days for a better pace.\", \"question\": \"How many days are enough for Thailand from Nepal?\"}, {\"answer\": \"Yes. Thailand, Malaysia and Singapore can be combined, but the route should be planned around flight timing, transfers, hotel locations and total travel days.\", \"question\": \"Can Thailand be combined with Malaysia or Singapore?\"}]'),(12,31,'bali','Bali','Bali','Indonesia',NULL,'international','/uploads/destinations/bali/bali_1766402663421.jpg','Discover the beauty and culture of Bali in Indonesia.','[]','Year-round','Varies','Easy to Moderate','/destinations/bali',1,'[321]','[]',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1,'2026-07-05 20:11:55','2026-07-05 20:11:55',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(13,32,'china','China','China','China',NULL,'international','/uploads/destinations/china/china_1766901366395.jpg','Discover the beauty and culture of China in China.','[]','Year-round','Varies','Easy to Moderate','/destinations/china',1,'[322]','[]',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1,'2026-07-05 20:11:55','2026-07-06 07:33:50','Plan China, Tibet and connected routes with practical timing, documentation, permit coordination and route clarity for travellers starting from Nepal.','Spring and autumn are generally preferred for comfortable travel and clearer route planning.','China-related routes often need stronger document, timing and permit coordination before booking. The route should be confirmed only after checking travel requirements.','[{\"body\": \"China and Tibet-related travel needs document clarity before hotel or flight commitment. Requirements can affect route, timing and group planning.\", \"icon\": \"Shield\", \"title\": \"Start with documents\"}, {\"body\": \"Long-distance sectors, border timing and guided-route rules should be understood early. This prevents unrealistic itinerary promises.\", \"icon\": \"Route\", \"title\": \"Plan route feasibility\"}, {\"body\": \"Guided support, transfers and communication matter more on cross-border routes than simple city breaks.\", \"icon\": \"Users\", \"title\": \"Choose support level\"}]','[{\"answer\": \"Yes, but document requirements, timing and route feasibility should be checked before confirming a package.\", \"question\": \"Can China routes be planned from Nepal?\"}, {\"answer\": \"Yes. Tibet-related travel usually requires more careful permit, route and support planning.\", \"question\": \"Is Tibet planning different from normal China travel?\"}]'),(14,33,'gandruk','Gandruk','Gandruk','Nepal',NULL,'nepal','/uploads/destinations/gandruk/gandruk_1766568489552.jpg','Discover the beauty and culture of Gandruk in Nepal.','[]','Year-round','Varies','Easy to Moderate','/destinations/gandruk',1,'[323]','[]',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1,'2026-07-05 20:11:55','2026-07-05 20:11:55',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(15,34,'nagarkot','Nagarkot','Nagarkot','Nepal',NULL,'nepal','/uploads/destinations/nagarkot/nagarkot_1766900084317.jpg','Discover the beauty and culture of Nagarkot in Nepal.','[]','Year-round','Varies','Easy to Moderate','/destinations/nagarkot',2,'[326, 327]','[]',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1,'2026-07-05 20:11:55','2026-07-05 20:11:55',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(16,35,'gorakhpur','Gorakhpur','Gorakhpur','Nepal',NULL,'nepal','/uploads/destinations/gorakhpur/gorakhpur_1766922735862.jpg','Discover the beauty and culture of Gorakhpur in Nepal.','[]','Year-round','Varies','Easy to Moderate','/destinations/gorakhpur',1,'[306]','[]',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1,'2026-07-05 20:11:55','2026-07-05 20:11:55',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(17,36,'9-day-ultimate-annapurna-sunrise-trek-ghorepani-poon-hill-beyond','Poon Hill','Poon Hill','Nepal',NULL,'nepal','/uploads/destinations/9-day-ultimate-annapurna-sunrise-trek-ghorepani-poon-hill-beyond/9-day-ultimate-annapurna-sunrise-trek-ghorepani-poon-hill-beyond_1769768713282.jpeg','Discover the beauty and culture of Poon Hill in Nepal.','[]','Year-round','Varies','Easy to Moderate','/destinations/9-day-ultimate-annapurna-sunrise-trek-ghorepani-poon-hill