INSERT INTO `testimonials` VALUES (1,8,'David Kim','david.kim@email.com','South Korea','Chitwan Safari Adventure',4,'Great Wildlife Safari','Excellent wildlife viewing opportunities in Chitwan National Park. We were lucky to spot a tiger during our jeep safari! The elephant breeding center visit was educational and the cultural program was entertaining. Good value for money.','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506794778202-cad84cf45f1d?q=80&w=150&h=150&fit=crop&crop=face','2024-11-12',1,1,'2024-11-15 15:30:00','2025-08-31 19:04:36'),(2,3,'Priya Sharma','priya.sharma@email.com','India','Chitwan Safari Adventure',4,'Amazing Wildlife Experience','The wildlife safari in Chitwan was fantastic! We saw rhinos, elephants, and so many bird species. The jungle lodge was comfortable and the naturalist guides were very informative. A great family adventure!','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1438761681033-6461ffad8d80?q=80&w=150&h=150&fit=crop&crop=face','2024-11-05',0,1,'2024-11-08 09:45:00','2024-11-08 09:45:00'),(3,10,'Robert Anderson','robert.anderson@email.com','United States','Everest Base Camp Trek',5,'Dream Come True','Reaching Everest Base Camp was a dream come true! The entire journey was well-planned and executed. Our Sherpa guide was amazing - so knowledgeable and encouraging. The views of Everest, Lhotse, and Nuptse were absolutely incredible. Thank you Zeo Tourism!','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507591064344-4c6ce005b128?q=80&w=150&h=150&fit=crop&crop=face','2024-10-25',1,1,'2024-10-30 17:45:00','2024-10-30 17:45:00'),(4,1,'Sarah Johnson','sarah.johnson@email.com','United States','Everest Base Camp Trek',5,'Life-changing Adventure','The Everest Base Camp trek with Zeo Tourism was absolutely incredible! The guides were knowledgeable, the accommodations were better than expected, and the entire experience exceeded my expectations. I\'ll never forget the sunrise from Kala Patthar!','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108755-2616b612b786?q=80&w=150&h=150&fit=crop&crop=face','2024-10-15',1,1,'2024-10-20 10:30:00','2024-10-20 10:30:00'),(5,6,'Hans Mueller','hans.mueller@email.com','Germany','Everest Base Camp Trek',4,'Well Organized Trek','Great organization and professional guides. The trek was challenging but manageable with proper preparation. The tea houses were comfortable and the food was surprisingly good. Would definitely book with Zeo Tourism again!','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500648767791-00dcc994a43e?q=80&w=150&h=150&fit=crop&crop=face','2024-10-02',0,1,'2024-10-08 13:45:00','2024-10-08 13:45:00'),(6,2,'Marco Rossi','marco.rossi@email.com','Italy','Annapurna Circuit Trek',5,'Perfect Organization','Zeo Tourism organized everything perfectly for our Annapurna Circuit trek. From permits to accommodations, everything was handled professionally. The local guides shared amazing stories about the culture and mountains. Highly recommended!','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?q=80&w=150&h=150&fit=crop&crop=face','2024-09-28',1,1,'2024-10-02 14:15:00','2024-10-02 14:15:00'),(7,7,'Lisa Chen','lisa.chen@email.com','Canada','Annapurna Base Camp Trek',5,'Breathtaking Mountain Views','The Annapurna Base Camp trek offered some of the most breathtaking mountain views I\'ve ever seen. The 360-degree panorama from ABC is simply stunning. Our guide was knowledgeable about local culture and mountain safety. Excellent service!','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1487412720507-e7ab37603c6f?q=80&w=150&h=150&fit=crop&crop=face','2024-09-15',0,1,'2024-09-20 08:15:00','2024-09-20 08:15:00'),(8,4,'James Wilson','james.wilson@email.com','Australia','Langtang Valley Trek',5,'Hidden Gem of Nepal','Langtang Valley is truly a hidden gem! Less crowded than other popular treks but equally beautiful. The Tamang culture, mountain views, and the famous cheese factory made this trek unforgettable. Zeo Tourism\'s service was excellent throughout.','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1472099645785-5658abf4ff4e?q=80&w=150&h=150&fit=crop&crop=face','2024-08-20',1,1,'2024-08-25 16:20:00','2024-08-25 16:20:00'),(9,9,'Maria Garcia','maria.garcia@email.com','Spain','Langtang Valley Trek',5,'Authentic Cultural Experience','The Langtang Valley trek provided an authentic cultural experience with the Tamang people. The hospitality was incredible, and learning about their traditions was fascinating. The mountain scenery was spectacular too. Highly recommend Zeo Tourism!','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1489424731084-a5d8b219a5bb?q=80&w=150&h=150&fit=crop&crop=face','2024-08-08',0,1,'2024-08-12 12:00:00','2024-08-12 12:00:00'),(10,5,'Emma Thompson','emma.thompson@email.com','United Kingdom','Kailash Mansarovar Yatra',5,'Spiritual Journey of a Lifetime','The Kailash Mansarovar Yatra was the most spiritual and transformative experience of my life. Despite the physical challenges, the journey was incredibly rewarding. The team at Zeo Tourism handled all logistics perfectly, allowing us to focus on the spiritual aspect.','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544005313-94ddf0286df2?q=80&w=150&h=150&fit=crop&crop=face','2024-07-12',1,1,'2024-07-18 11:30:00','2024-07-18 11:30:00');
/*!40000 ALTER TABLE `testimonials` ENABLE KEYS */;
UNLOCK TABLES;

